These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, lawyer, bartender, project-manager
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, bellflower, azalea, marigold
1. the photographer is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
2. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left##1
3. the person who growsazalea is between the person who growsbellflower and the lawyer##2
4. the project-manager is on the far left##1
5. the bartender is between the lawyer and the photographer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Job   | project-manager         | lawyer   | bartender | photographer       |
| Flower      | marigold | begonia | azalea   | bellflower |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
There 4 different types of food: kale, pepper, zucchini, grapefruit
4 different games are played: bridge, mah-jongg, whist, poker
1. the person playing poker is between the person eating zucchini and the person playing mah-jongg##2
2. the person eating grapefruit is on the far right##1
3. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
4. the person eating kale is on the left of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Food         | pepper | kale | zucchini | grapefruit |
| Game   | mah-jongg    | poker   | bridge | whist       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, june, february, august
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, sprite, soy-milk
1. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking coffee and the person who's birthday is in june##2
3. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Birthday          | august    | july | june   | february  |
| Beverage   | coffee | sprite   | soy-milk | iced-tea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, zombie, superhero, mystery
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, hot-chocolate, iced-tea
1. the person drinking cola is the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person drinking coffee and the person watching mystery movies##2
3. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre     | mystery   | time-travel    | superhero       | zombie   |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | iced-tea | coffee | cola |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, august, may, july
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, orchid, bellflower, balloon-flower
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person who growsbellflower is on the far left##1
3. the person who growsmarigold is on the far right##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who growsmarigold and the person who growsorchid##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Birthday   | february        | may | july  | august |
| Flower      | bellflower | orchid  | balloon-flower | marigold    |

