.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, zombie, horror, adventure
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, july, october, may
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is the person who's birthday is in january##1
5. the person watching horror movies is between the person watching scientific movies and the person watching zombie movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie     | horror           | scientific | adventure  |
| Birthday         | january | may | july   | october |

