.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, pomegranate, tomato, kale
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, sudoku, cooking, skydiving
1. the person eating pomegranate is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
5. the person eating blueberry is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person eating tomato##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Food   | kale   | pomegranate | blueberry | tomato      |
| Hobby     | cooking | filmmaking    | sudoku  | skydiving |

