.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, funk, dubstep, classical
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, brown, purple, amber
1. the person who likes blood-red is the fan funk##1
2. the person who likes brown is between the fan dubstep and the person who likes purple##2
3. the fan punk is on the far left##1
4. the person who likes blood-red is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre       | punk | classical | dubstep     | funk   |
| Color   | purple   | brown     | amber | blood-red |

