.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, poppy, daisy, orchid
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, reading, photography, cooking
1. the person who growsdaisy is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who growsrose##2
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
3. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
5. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Flower         | poppy | daisy | rose | orchid |
| Hobby   | board-games         | cooking       | reading    | photography         |

