.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, architect, software-developer, dressmaker
4 different games are played: chess, poker, bridge, domino
1. the person playing poker is on the right of the dressmaker##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the right of the software-developer##1
3. the bartender is on the right of the architect##1
4. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing poker##1
5. the person playing poker is between the architect and the person playing domino##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Job    | dressmaker   | software-developer      | architect   | bartender  |
| Game   | domino | poker | bridge | chess |

