.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, february, may, march
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, mexican, spanish, argentine
1. the argentine is on the right of the mexican##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in april##2
3. the mexican is on the right of the spanish##1
4. the spanish is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Birthday          | april     | february | march   | may        |
| Nationality   | pakistani | spanish   | mexican | argentine |

