.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
City: miami, new-york, liverpool, hamburg
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, iris, daffodil, aconite
1. the person who growsdaffodil is the person traveling to new-york##1
2. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
3. the person who growsbegonia is the person traveling to miami##1
4. the person traveling to liverpool is the person who growsiris##1
5. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
6. the person who growsiris is between the person traveling to new-york and the person traveling to hamburg##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| City         | new-york | liverpool | hamburg | miami |
| Flower   | daffodil          | iris     | aconite  | begonia     |

