.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-13::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, bolivar, blend, dannemann
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, electronic, soul, punk
1. the fan soul is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
2. the dannemann-smoker is between the fan punk and the dunhill-smoker##2
3. the fan electronic is on the far right##1
4. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the fan soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Cigar           | dunhill | dannemann | bolivar | blend     |
| Music-Genre   | country   | soul    | punk   | electronic |

