The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, woodworking, writing, traveling
1. the person eating garlic is the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
3. the person eating corn is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person eating corn##1
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Food           | zucchini | corn | mango | garlic |
| Hobby   | woodworking   | rock-climbing | traveling         | writing |

