2. the australian is on the far left##1
3. the havana-smoker is between the australian and the cain-smoker##2
4. the montecristo-smoker is the australian##1
5. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Cigar       | montecristo | havana | cain | ritmeester |
| Nationality   | australian    | american  | polish    | turkish       |

