2. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
3. the person traveling to liverpool is the person who growsaconite##1
4. the person who growsdaffodil is between the person traveling to prague and the person traveling to venice##2
5. the person traveling to venice is the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| City   | liverpool   | prague   | london | venice |
| Flower         | aconite | daisy | daffodil     | lily    |

