.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, azure, amber, light-blue
House: farmhouse, modern, wooden, gothic-revival
1. the modern house is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes lilac is between the farmhouse house and the person who likes light-blue##2
3. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
4. the person who likes azure is on the far right##1
5. the person who likes azure is on the right of the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Color   | amber    | light-blue     | lilac | azure |
| House     | modern | gothic-revival | wooden       | farmhouse     |

 